properties.title: Southern Dream-Brand
properties.description: SOUTHERN DREAM is a brand new, luxurious, pond-side treehouse in the woods.  It is the ideal place to spend your honeymoon or a romantic getaway with your love.  Indoors, SOUTHERN DREAM has massive picture windows, a large walk-in rain shower, a fully stocked kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Outside, you’ll enjoy relaxing in the hot tub, resting on the swing bed, walking the trails, or fishing at the pond.  Make SOUTHERN DREAM your own and fall in love all over again.

properties.title: COUNTRY CABIN
properties.description: BEAUTIFUL COZY CABIN FOR YOUR FAMILY!!! This beautifully decorated 7 sq ft. cabin has everything you need for your perfect getaway. Just a 45 minute drive north of McKinney located on 2.5 acres. You can sit back and enjoy the view of the trees while rocking of the front porch with your morning coffee. Located only 10 miles from Lake Bonham, this cabin has a full kitchen equipped with everything you need for a country escape

properties.title: Waterfront Kabana
properties.description: Our Kabanas are waterfront, single-room tiny homes with stunning lake views. Each Kabana is equipped with a queen bed, small fridge, Bluetooth speaker, indoor/outdoor seating, super unique fire-pit, and an outdoor kitchen complete with a BBQ grill. The AC unit will keep you chilly in the summer and warm in the winter and the electrical includes USB charging stations. Linens are provided for the beds and the bathroom and shower facilities are a short walk away

properties.title: Lake Texoma Cabin
properties.description: Kick back in a beautiful luxury cabin overlooking a small lake that is shared between guests of this Cabin and the Tiny Home resort. The covered patio, dock, and peninsula are strictly for the use of guests of this cabin. This home has granite counters, leather furniture, family size dining table, flatscreen TV, walk-in shower, refrigerator, oven, cooktop, and microwave. 2 large covered outdoor areas are perfect for BBQs.

properties.title: Pottsboro Cabin
properties.description: Sitting only a mile away from the shores of Lake Texoma, this Pottsboro vacation rental boasts 2 bedrooms, a loft, and 2 bathrooms. Rent a boat for a day on the water for tubing, swimming, and fishing or take a hike along the trails of Eisenhower State Park. Tanglewood Resort's golf course sits 2 miles away from the cabin where you can practice your swing or delight your taste buds at Homestead Vineyard & Winery. Spend your evenings sitting around the cabin's fire pit to make s'mores and stargaze

properties.title: Rancho De Los Arbres
properties.description: Our Denton County country guest house which is located in the heart of the DFW Metroplex…approximately 40 miles northwest of downtown Dallas, 40 miles northeast of downtown Fort Worth and 60 miles from Arlington. You will have access to the home and private heated pool.

properties.title: Lazy Acres Farmhouse
properties.description: Long or short term rental. This cutie of a farm house was built in 1841 and is one of the oldest homes in Collin County.  Wrap around covered porch with a swing to watch the sunset or  overlook the 40 plus acres of rolling meadows and trees surrounding the home.  You could possibly spot some deer, wild turkey, or hear the coyotes howl at the full moon.  This home is very close to wedding venues, Hurricane Creek Country Club, and a short drive to downtown McKinney.

properties.title: Mom's Tiny House Retreat
properties.description: A peaceful private prairie escape. Wildflowers and songbird hawks drifting above the trees Walking paths, a creek in the spring Cathedral of trees with a tree swing. Full kitchen (no microwave)

properties.title: The Shack
properties.description: The SHACK is an eclectic space that evolved from our love of building with repurposed materials. Includes old cedar fence pickets, floor tile is made from an old tree. As The SHACK took shape we decided that the theme is sort of anything redneck construction including duck tape, even has a chain link clothes line. With all the amenities of course!! We hand built the custom waterfall sink faucet. Bed is held up w/log chains, tile shower that resembles a quilt w/ exposed copper plumbing.

properties.title: Pet-Friendly Cabin
properties.description: This stunning and spacious cabin is the ideal location for a Blue Ridge vacation. Outdoor living meets luxury with a hot tub, outdoor fire pit, and beautiful views of the mountains. This is the perfect romantic getaway or place to create memories with family and friends. Plus, enjoy scenic drives to the many nearby local attractions.

properties.title: Estes Retreat
properties.description: Cabin 1 is one of the original Cabins within the Mountain Village community. The interior decorators spared no expense designing the beautiful décor. Mountain Village at Lake Estes is a brand new upscale residential-resort community highlighting by the surrounding lake and stunning mountain views. This cabin features 1,577 square feet featuring 2 master suites, 2 full bathrooms & 1 powder room, balcony, loft, living area with 25-foot-tall fireplace, state of the art kitchen, dining area, BBQ grill and a patio that features another stone fireplace and a 6-person jacuzzi. This cabin will sleep 6 people comfortably. This cabin has dramatic floor to ceiling windows spanning 25 feet, the cabin also has heating and cooling for your comfort.

properties.title: Cabin hosted by Vacasa Georgia
properties.description: Find peace, relaxation, and spectacular autumn color at this four-bedroom Mineral Bluff home, a woodsy retreat with a private hot tub, an expansive and partially screened deck and balcony, and a gorgeous location overlooking the mountains of North Georgia.
